snippet.title: Nippon Marathon Trailer: Out December 17th 2018
snippet.description:
Nippon Marathon out December 17th 2018 on PC, PS4, XBox & Nintendo Switch. 

Follow Wedy Jones, official reporter for Nippon Marathon on Twitter: www.twitter.com/NipponMarathon

Published by PQube Games (http://pqube.co.uk/games/)

Created by OnionSoupInteractive (www.onionsoupinteractive.com)

Music by: Robert Ruby Music (www.robertrubymusic.com) & Diana Garnet (http://dianagarnet.jp/)/ www.twitter.com/Tonkhaikichi
